imit the number of playtesters that we will take on, so please reply as soon as possible. If you do not hear back from me, it means we filled the slots and my apologies in advance for not giving you a reply. <br><br>Also, we will be demonstrating the game at the Seattle EQ Fan Faire, those of you attending please look for us there! <br><br>Regards, <br><br>Steve Wieck <br>Sword &amp; Sorcery Studio <br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.swordsorcery.com">www.swordsorcery.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.EQrpg.com">www.EQrpg.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unadiabrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nadia brell</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~karl23/ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#FFFF66>Board Moderator</font><br><font color=#A0B0E0>&#60;Grey Silence&#62;</font></span><br>  Posts: 1307<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/10/02 9:03:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm70.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=140.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Everquest: the tabletop game</span><hr size=1> at their merchandise site <br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqrpg.com/eqmoreinfo.html">www.eqrpg.com/eqmoreinfo.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <br><br>they say that the players handbook and critter guide will be available in july and august <br><br><br>the gamemaster guide wont be out until october <br><br><br>heres a snippet from creature guide marketing <br><!--EZCODE AU